1.3.name: wordpress/coffee-time
1.3.description: Coffee Time is a minimalist, soft, smooth and responsive WordPress theme with device-agnostic layout, focusing on content and delightful reading. Suitable for collaborative blogs and long articles. A WordPress theme to help you read and write things that matter.
